des:
The robot can clean its own mop fabric and has fully-automatic mopping system:Self-washing system,Pressurized mopping,Separation of dust and purification,LIDAR SLAM,Snail touch(waggled side brush),Multi-function APP,Disposable dust bag

Note:only supports english users.

To get stated,"Enable Skill" in Alexa,link your veniibot account and discover your devices.

Use the device name to identify your device,

Supported Device:N1,N1 MAX ,and so on.

Supported Action:
//set volume
set the volume of the veniibot to 50
set the volume of the veniibot to 0
//start clean
set the veniibot to clean
//pause 
set the veniibot to pause 
//charge
set the veniibot to charge
//clean fabric
set the veniibot to wash
//set mop mode
set the veniibot to mop mode
//set sweep mode
set the veniibot to sweep mode
//set mop and sweep mode 
set the venii to mix mode

//set fans quiet mode
set the veniibot to quiet mode
//set fans standard mode
set the veniibot to standard mode 
//set fans enhance mode
set the veniibot to enhance mode
//set fans max mode
set the veniibot to max mode
